thread.title: BRIEF-Tal Consolidated Inc Files for IPO of up to $17.3 Million - SEC filing

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Tal Consolidated Inc Files for IPO of up to $17.3 Million - SEC filing

organizations.name: brief-tal consolidated inc files for ipo

text:
Jan 17 (Reuters) -
* TAL CONSOLIDATED INC FILES FOR IPO OF UP TO $17.3 MILLION - SEC FILING
* TAL CONSOLIDATED INC SAYS IT INTENDS TO APPLY TO HAVE ITS COMMON STOCK LISTED ON NASDAQ UNDER THE SYMBOL “TCL”
* TAL CONSOLIDATED INC SAYS JOSEPH GUNNAR & CO IS UNDERWRITER TO IPO
* TAL CONSOLIDATED INC SAYS PROPOSED IPO PRICE IS AN ESTIMATE SOLELY FOR CALCULATING SEC REGISTRATION FEE Source text: ( bit.ly/2mPWwTc )
